  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare acid-base changes during hemodialysis treatments with a standard
      dialysis bath versus a lower bicarbonate dialysis bath, and aims to define the factors that
      limit equilibration of the bicarbonate concentration in a patient's blood with that in the
      dialysate.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
